title: previously Gold ADC/JG , looking for Duo who is Silver/Bronze to do ranked duo with to climb
body:
After having 3 leavers during provisionals and a few losses i got left in B4, since climbed to b2 but its beating my head against a wall. Need a decent team mate to work up with, get out of shit elo with and maybe even keep going for gold+ 

Previously been silver and gold in earlier seasons

replies.body: I really want to just make silver if you could help me that would be great :D
Want to climb aswell and me if you want, i pretty much main supp
Im looking to get higher, silver last season, add if you want duo
I'm in the same boat, high silver, fighting back out of bronze from horrible placement.
